    {
      "type": "answer",
      "text": "Found it. **ToggleKeys** (Flags: 62) and **StickyKeys** (Flags: 510) are both **enabled**. That's the beeping/noise. Let me disable them.",
      "timestamp": 1782379198975
    },
    {
      "type": "thought",
      "text": "Let me analyze the flags:\n\n1. **ToggleKeys** - `Flags: 62`\n   - Bit 0x01 (1) = Feature is ON\n   - Bit 0x02 (2) = Confirm key press (beep when toggled)\n   - Bit 0x04 (4) = Play sound\n   \n   62 in binary = 0011 1110 = bits 1,2,3,4,5 are set\n   - Bit 1 (0x02) = ToggleKeys is enabled\n   \n   Actually, let me recalculate. 62 = 32+16+8+4+2 = 0b00111110\n   - Bit 1 (0x02) = YES - ToggleKeys is ON\n   - This means ToggleKeys IS enabled and will beep when Caps Lock, Num Lock, Scroll Lock are toggled\n\n2. **StickyKeys** - `Flags: 510`\n   - 510 = 256+128+64+32+16+8+4+2 = 0b0001 1111 1110\n   - Bit 1 (0x02) = YES - StickyKeys is ON\n   - This means StickyKeys IS enabled\n\n3. **FilterKeys** - No entry found, so it's likely disabled or using defaults\n\nSo both ToggleKeys and StickyKeys are enabled. Let me disable them both. Also, I should check the keyboard indicators setting which is set to `2` (NumLock ON at boot).\n\nLet me fix these by setting the flags to disabled (0).",
      "timestamp": 1782379201577
    },
    {
      "type": "action",
      "tool": "bash",
      "code": "{\"command\": \"Start-Process powershell -Verb RunAs -ArgumentList \\\"-NoProfile -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -Command\\\", \\\"Set-ItemProperty -Path 'HKCU:\\\\Control Panel\\\\Accessibility\\\\ToggleKeys' -Name 'Flags' -Value '0'; Set-ItemProperty -Path 'HKCU:\\\\Control Panel\\\\Accessibility\\\\StickyKeys' -Name 'Flags' -Value '0'; Set-ItemProperty -Path 'HKCU:\\\\Control Panel\\\\Accessibility\\\\KeyboardResponse' -Name 'Flags' -Value '0'; Set-ItemProperty -Path 'HKCU:\\\\Control Panel\\\\Accessibility\\\\Keyboard Response' -Name 'Flags' -Value '0'; Write-Host 'Done'\\\" -Wait 2>&1\", \"description\": \"Disable ToggleKeys and StickyKeys via UAC\", \"timeout\": 30000}",
      "output": "(no output)",
      "status": "success",
      "timestamp": 1782379208947
