      "type": "thought",
      "text": "The user is in a Zoom meeting and can't sign out or restart. The registry changes they made should take effect for new sessions, but they need a way to apply them without signing out. \n\nLet me try a few things:\n1. Use SystemParametersInfo API to apply the changes immediately\n2. Use a broadcast message to update the settings\n3. Try to programmatically send the accessibility setting change notification\n\nThe registry changes are written but need a broadcast or session update to take effect. Let me try using SystemParametersInfo or sending a WM_SETTINGCHANGE message.",
      "timestamp": 1782379323097
